              Each of the three levels of government has a different impact on a citizens life, so each represenative is chunked into their proper group.
              Finding a rep is the same process as finding a contact in Messenger or Whatsapp.
              I borrowed the familiar layout such that Briana or Terry could use GovContact as they would any other messaging app. 
            .display-flex
               .grid-6
                 +img("gc_home.png", "home")
               .grid-6
