            +subheader("Everything you need to know")
            span.
              Based on the online research and interviews with government employees, the contact information for each rep is ordered by availability and effectiveness.
              Although no political party is mentioned, Briana and Terry can understand how each of their reps stands on the issues. 
            .display-flex
               .grid-6
                 +img("rep.png", "rep")
               .grid-6
                 +img("rep-expanded.png", "rep expanded")
