              | In this manner, I was learned how to explore brand beyond the expected to create something unique.
            +listItem("Knowing what type to prototype")
              | I utilized two types of prototypes: code prototypes and click-through prototypes.
              | The web prototype made in React.js was useful for testing how someone would be most likely to interact with the app
              | However programming took up a lot of time compared to the click-through protoype, which I could focus more on the design of GovContact.
              | The lesson I learned was when to use each kind of prototype.
          
